name: test
sql: create or replace view test.test as SELECT COUNT(*) FROM( SELECT knowledgeinterlinker_name, softwareinterlinker_name, COUNT(DISTINCT(coproductionprocess_id)) AS IN_PROCESSES FROM elastic2.logs.log WHERE action LIKE 'CREATE' AND model LIKE 'ASSET' GROUP BY knowledgeinterlinker_name, softwareinterlinker_name ) WHERE IN_PROCESSES > 1
